1
00:01:13,010 --> 00:01:14,249
Try the dishes cooked by Wang.

2
00:01:15,169 --> 00:01:16,010
Are you

3
00:01:16,130 --> 00:01:18,169
taking care of me as if I were Li Feiyuan?

4
00:01:19,050 --> 00:01:20,130
Don't mention her.

5
00:01:20,449 --> 00:01:21,650
She's fierce.

6
00:01:21,809 --> 00:01:23,290
You're much more friendly.

7
00:01:23,969 --> 00:01:25,650
She's the daughter of a noble family.

8
00:01:26,050 --> 00:01:26,969
She's noble,

9
00:01:27,490 --> 00:01:29,690
not fierce as you said.

10
00:01:30,609 --> 00:01:32,249
Anyway, don't be possessed

11
00:01:32,329 --> 00:01:33,010
by her memory energy.

12
00:01:33,329 --> 00:01:35,130
My boss looks haggard these days.

13
00:01:36,969 --> 00:01:39,169
What does your boss do

14
00:01:39,570 --> 00:01:40,410
when he's alone at home?

15
00:01:41,410 --> 00:01:41,930
Let me show you.

16
00:01:43,130 --> 00:01:43,889
Playing with his phone.

17
00:01:46,050 --> 00:01:46,770
Fixing his phone.

18
00:01:47,650 --> 00:01:48,690
Can't live without his phone.

19
00:01:49,850 --> 00:01:51,210
Our boss is anxious.

20
00:01:51,570 --> 00:01:53,010
He's afraid you'll abandon him again.

21
00:01:54,729 --> 00:01:55,690
Childish.

22
00:01:56,490 --> 00:01:58,010
I've only been gone for two days.

23
00:01:58,169 --> 00:01:58,729
You're making it sound like

24
00:01:58,850 --> 00:02:00,169
I've been gone for two months.

25
00:02:00,490 --> 00:02:02,169
Our neocortex distribution

26
00:02:02,369 --> 00:02:03,249
differs from humans,

27
00:02:03,529 --> 00:02:05,010
so does our perception of time.

28
00:02:05,290 --> 00:02:06,290
Once we get used to companionship

29
00:02:06,570 --> 00:02:07,729
after a long time of loneliness,

30
00:02:08,049 --> 00:02:09,090
the anxiety of separation

31
00:02:09,250 --> 00:02:10,290
will be even stronger.

32
00:02:15,010 --> 00:02:15,570
Got it.

33
00:02:15,970 --> 00:02:16,850
I won't leave him.

34
00:02:25,329 --> 00:02:26,810
Why don't you tell Miss Jiang

35
00:02:27,290 --> 00:02:28,489
that you made the dishes yourself?

36
00:02:30,929 --> 00:02:31,889
I'm still learning.

37
00:02:32,449 --> 00:02:34,810
Now I'm testing the taste.

38
00:02:41,570 --> 00:02:42,010
Old Wang.

39
00:02:45,929 --> 00:02:46,410
Okay.

40
00:02:47,410 --> 00:02:48,209
If something goes wrong,

41
00:02:48,609 --> 00:02:49,769
I'll take the blame.

42
00:04:30,209 --> 00:04:30,730
Are you

43
00:04:31,170 --> 00:04:31,889
still there?

44
00:04:34,409 --> 00:04:35,170
What's on your mind?

45
00:04:37,769 --> 00:04:40,409
I'm in pain when I'm unconscious.

46
00:04:41,930 --> 00:04:43,730
How are you doing?

47
00:04:44,490 --> 00:04:45,170
I'm fine.

48
00:04:46,769 --> 00:04:48,649
But your emotions are turbulent,

49
00:04:49,170 --> 00:04:49,969
and woke me up.

50
00:04:53,610 --> 00:04:54,649
I want to know

51
00:04:55,449 --> 00:04:56,610
what you feel

52
00:04:57,329 --> 00:04:58,529
about Cang Feng.

53
00:05:00,130 --> 00:05:01,050
Why do you ask?

54
00:05:02,329 --> 00:05:03,529
When we were in the dream,

55
00:05:03,649 --> 00:05:04,730
you told me

56
00:05:05,449 --> 00:05:06,690
you like Lu Zhiyu.

57
00:05:08,370 --> 00:05:10,810
You know me better than I know myself.

58
00:05:12,130 --> 00:05:12,969
But

59
00:05:13,649 --> 00:05:14,409
if your affection

60
00:05:14,529 --> 00:05:16,730
stems from your past with him,

61
00:05:17,610 --> 00:05:18,209
[then]

62
00:05:19,529 --> 00:05:20,769
[it's not real love.]

63
00:05:21,490 --> 00:05:22,730
[I'm just your past,]

64
00:05:23,810 --> 00:05:26,010
[I can't control your present and future.]

65
00:05:27,370 --> 00:05:28,769
[Instead of talking to yourself here,]

66
00:05:29,570 --> 00:05:30,889
[you'd better ask him yourself.]

67
00:05:31,810 --> 00:05:33,089
[If you're wavering,]

68
00:05:34,409 --> 00:05:36,130
[I'll have to come out and fight for you.]

69
00:05:38,969 --> 00:05:39,649
Li Feiyuan,

70
00:05:40,570 --> 00:05:42,130
although you always talk tough,

71
00:05:42,570 --> 00:05:43,570
I think

72
00:05:44,529 --> 00:05:46,529
you've been guiding us all along.

73
00:05:48,610 --> 00:05:51,289
If we can take turns waking up,

74
00:05:51,769 --> 00:05:52,490
then it seems...

75
00:05:55,610 --> 00:05:56,769
Still not willing?

76
00:06:02,930 --> 00:06:04,050
I'll do it.

77
00:06:04,969 --> 00:06:06,610
I need to adapt to human habits.

78
00:06:07,769 --> 00:06:08,649
Start with household chores.

79
00:06:11,329 --> 00:06:13,289
Confession is the most important part.

80
00:06:14,490 --> 00:06:15,289
Chores?

81
00:06:18,289 --> 00:06:18,849
Bro,

82
00:06:19,010 --> 00:06:19,849
does she love you?

83
00:06:22,969 --> 00:06:23,570
I love her.

84
00:06:25,849 --> 00:06:26,610
She doesn't love me.

85
00:06:30,170 --> 00:06:31,170
She stays by my side

86
00:06:31,370 --> 00:06:32,570
because of the brand.

87
00:06:33,529 --> 00:06:34,529
Once the brand disappears,

88
00:06:35,209 --> 00:06:36,050
she will leave.

89
00:06:37,050 --> 00:06:37,730
You believe that?

90
00:06:38,889 --> 00:06:39,690
She said it herself.

91
00:06:43,570 --> 00:06:44,810
Human emotions

92
00:06:45,250 --> 00:06:46,130
are complicated.

93
00:06:47,289 --> 00:06:48,289
Women...

94
00:06:49,490 --> 00:06:50,089
You'll understand

95
00:06:50,409 --> 00:06:52,209
after enduring more hardships.

96
00:07:00,089 --> 00:07:01,289
[It seems very cold outside.]

97
00:07:12,649 --> 00:07:14,409
[If I go to find him dressed like this,]

98
00:07:15,250 --> 00:07:16,730
[he won't laugh at me, will he?]

99
00:07:27,409 --> 00:07:29,010
Mom won't come back,

100
00:07:29,610 --> 00:07:30,130
right?

101
00:07:33,969 --> 00:07:35,769
Someone will come to pick you up soon.

102
00:07:36,570 --> 00:07:37,209
Sir,

103
00:07:37,409 --> 00:07:39,409
I don't even know your name.

104
00:07:43,930 --> 00:07:44,570
I forgot.

105
00:07:45,889 --> 00:07:47,010
You have such a bad memory.

106
00:07:49,050 --> 00:07:50,209
Then I'll give you a name.

107
00:07:54,170 --> 00:07:55,490
Your name is

108
00:07:57,050 --> 00:07:57,610
Yu.

109
00:07:59,010 --> 00:07:59,490
Okay.

110
00:08:01,050 --> 00:08:02,810
I'll come back to see you later.

111
00:08:14,969 --> 00:08:15,730
[It turns out]

112
00:08:16,769 --> 00:08:18,050
[our story]

113
00:08:19,050 --> 00:08:20,730
[started from that time.]

114
00:08:26,730 --> 00:08:27,730
Why are you still up this late?

115
00:08:36,010 --> 00:08:37,049
Can you tell

116
00:08:37,569 --> 00:08:38,850
if I'm Jiang Yue

117
00:08:39,370 --> 00:08:40,490
or Li Feiyuan?

118
00:08:41,809 --> 00:08:42,289
Of course.

119
00:08:42,769 --> 00:08:43,289
Why?

120
00:08:43,649 --> 00:08:44,769
We look exactly the same.

121
00:08:45,330 --> 00:08:46,569
When I was in Hidden Edge,

122
00:08:46,730 --> 00:08:47,490
my master

123
00:08:48,289 --> 00:08:49,450
would tease me when she was happy,

124
00:08:49,730 --> 00:08:50,889
and punish me when she was angry.

125
00:08:51,929 --> 00:08:53,049
I lived each day

126
00:08:53,130 --> 00:08:54,490
in constant fear.

127
00:08:55,610 --> 00:08:56,330
Like this.

128
00:08:59,490 --> 00:09:01,929
It seems Jiang Yue doesn't have this authority.

129
00:09:07,010 --> 00:09:08,450
I'll take you somewhere.

130
00:09:09,289 --> 00:09:09,889
Where to?

131
00:09:10,730 --> 00:09:11,610
You'll know soon.

132
00:09:12,730 --> 00:09:14,289
If you don't tell me, I won't go.

133
00:09:20,250 --> 00:09:21,689
Birthday gift.

134
00:09:28,970 --> 00:09:29,649
Hold tight.

135
00:09:46,010 --> 00:09:46,850
It's so beautiful.

136
00:09:47,450 --> 00:09:47,970
Look up.

137
00:09:50,809 --> 00:09:51,850
Is that Orion?

138
00:09:54,169 --> 00:09:55,090
Southwest of it

139
00:09:55,610 --> 00:09:56,929
is Alpha Canis Majoris.

140
00:09:58,210 --> 00:09:59,889
Sounds like your hometown.

141
00:10:01,809 --> 00:10:02,409
It's possible.

142
00:10:04,250 --> 00:10:06,289
Are you expressing homesickness here?

143
00:10:07,010 --> 00:10:08,169
You're not thinking

144
00:10:08,490 --> 00:10:10,409
of suddenly going back one day

145
00:10:11,330 --> 00:10:13,330
and come back every few hundred years?

146
00:10:15,490 --> 00:10:16,649
Canis Major is

147
00:10:16,850 --> 00:10:17,809
6.5 light-years away from us.

148
00:10:18,370 --> 00:10:19,250
Even if I'm fast,

149
00:10:20,289 --> 00:10:21,090
I can't fly there.

150
00:10:23,769 --> 00:10:24,370
Lu Zhiyu,

151
00:10:26,689 --> 00:10:27,769
how long

152
00:10:28,289 --> 00:10:29,409
is your life?

153
00:10:33,889 --> 00:10:34,689
Thousands of years.

154
00:10:37,169 --> 00:10:39,169
Can you bite me?

155
00:10:40,210 --> 00:10:41,649
I want to be a werewolf

156
00:10:42,689 --> 00:10:43,889
to live forever,

157
00:10:44,130 --> 00:10:45,250
travel around the world,

158
00:10:45,569 --> 00:10:46,769
and be financially free.

159
00:10:53,409 --> 00:10:54,250
You wish.

160
00:10:55,610 --> 00:10:56,409
I will also grow old.

161
00:10:58,370 --> 00:10:59,769
But for me,

162
00:11:00,889 --> 00:11:02,370
it's already a long time.

163
00:11:05,929 --> 00:11:07,850
Sirius has a lifespan of a billion years.

164
00:11:08,850 --> 00:11:09,689
Compared to it,

165
00:11:10,610 --> 00:11:12,730
we are just like mayflies.

166
00:11:14,889 --> 00:11:16,010
So for me,

167
00:11:17,850 --> 00:11:19,010
cherishing the present is enough.

168
00:11:20,730 --> 00:11:22,490
I just thought of one thing

169
00:11:22,569 --> 00:11:24,010
to cherish the present.

170
00:11:26,769 --> 00:11:27,330
What?

171
00:11:54,569 --> 00:11:55,130
Brother,

172
00:11:55,569 --> 00:11:56,649
didn't you run away from home?

173
00:11:57,250 --> 00:11:58,970
You came back crying because you were out of money.

174
00:11:59,610 --> 00:12:00,689
Don't fight in front of me.

175
00:12:01,450 --> 00:12:01,970
A Che.

176
00:12:08,049 --> 00:12:08,490
Brother,

177
00:12:11,769 --> 00:12:12,649
where did you sleep last night?

178
00:12:14,569 --> 00:12:15,090
In the tree.

179
00:12:15,370 --> 00:12:15,970
In the tree?

180
00:12:17,610 --> 00:12:18,370
Be careful not to catch a cold.

181
00:12:19,730 --> 00:12:20,450
You're reading.

182
00:12:23,010 --> 00:12:24,289
Do you have to be her servant?

183
00:12:27,210 --> 00:12:29,490
Jiang Yue and I are partners certified by the Brand.

184
00:12:30,049 --> 00:12:31,809
It's my duty to take care of her.

185
00:12:32,409 --> 00:12:33,289
Let's have breakfast together.

186
00:12:40,769 --> 00:12:41,250
How is it?

187
00:12:44,330 --> 00:12:45,169
Chef level.

188
00:12:54,730 --> 00:12:55,730
I'm going on a trip today

189
00:12:56,569 --> 00:12:57,330
to deal with

190
00:12:57,569 --> 00:13:00,090
the trouble Xie Chen has brought to Black Rock Island.

191
00:13:03,409 --> 00:13:05,049
Are you ready?

192
00:13:05,409 --> 00:13:06,049
Don't worry.

193
00:13:06,529 --> 00:13:08,330
I won't put your brother in any danger.

194
00:13:09,649 --> 00:13:10,569
Zhang San and Li Si

195
00:13:10,769 --> 00:13:11,809
will keep you safe.

196
00:13:13,970 --> 00:13:14,569
Okay.

197
00:13:19,210 --> 00:13:20,689
What a nice day.

198
00:13:20,889 --> 00:13:22,769
It's a pity to stay at home.

199
00:13:23,809 --> 00:13:25,730
How about playing beach volleyball?

200
00:13:28,490 --> 00:13:30,490
But do we have enough people?

201
00:13:35,730 --> 00:13:37,610
I do want to go to the beach.

202
00:13:38,730 --> 00:13:39,929
We have the same goal.

203
00:13:40,370 --> 00:13:41,289
Why not cooperate?

204
00:13:42,769 --> 00:13:43,689
Here's my business card.

205
00:13:44,130 --> 00:13:45,610
My phone number is on it.

206
00:13:46,049 --> 00:13:46,809
You trick Jiang Yue

207
00:13:46,889 --> 00:13:48,130
out of your brother's side.

208
00:13:48,610 --> 00:13:49,769
I'll talk to her

209
00:13:49,970 --> 00:13:51,049
to persuade her to give up.

210
00:13:52,169 --> 00:13:53,010
Whether to form an alliance or not,

211
00:13:53,370 --> 00:13:54,330
it's up to you.

212
00:13:55,210 --> 00:13:56,409
I always go it alone,

213
00:13:56,649 --> 00:13:57,769
never forming alliances with others.

214
00:14:10,889 --> 00:14:11,689
Are we going whale watching or not?

215
00:14:14,330 --> 00:14:16,210
You can see whales at sea right now.

216
00:14:22,610 --> 00:14:24,090
Whales at the dock?

217
00:14:25,090 --> 00:14:25,649
Where are they?

218
00:14:27,409 --> 00:14:27,929
Over there.

219
00:14:43,610 --> 00:14:45,490
You went to so much trouble to bring me out

220
00:14:45,809 --> 00:14:47,090
just to introduce me to her?

221
00:14:51,689 --> 00:14:53,049
Qin Yaxin,

222
00:14:54,330 --> 00:14:55,210
you still remember me.

223
00:14:56,250 --> 00:14:58,210
It seems I'm quite charming.

224
00:14:59,210 --> 00:15:00,210
What do you want now?

225
00:15:00,490 --> 00:15:01,610
Didn't you leave?

226
00:15:01,769 --> 00:15:02,689
Why are you back?

227
00:15:03,569 --> 00:15:04,610
I'm here to tell you

228
00:15:04,769 --> 00:15:06,250
to give up.

229
00:15:06,450 --> 00:15:07,809
Don't compete with me for a man.

230
00:15:10,970 --> 00:15:12,049
Before I get mad,

231
00:15:12,210 --> 00:15:13,330
you'd better listen to me.

232
00:15:13,889 --> 00:15:15,130
I'll give you two choices.

233
00:15:15,689 --> 00:15:16,169
First,

234
00:15:16,529 --> 00:15:17,490
leave Lu Zhiyu.

235
00:15:17,929 --> 00:15:18,409
Second,

236
00:15:19,130 --> 00:15:20,409
I'll throw you into the sea to feed the fish.

237
00:15:20,809 --> 00:15:21,370
Which one do you choose?

238
00:15:22,529 --> 00:15:23,289
I'll leave him.

239
00:15:27,090 --> 00:15:27,889
So obedient.

240
00:15:28,929 --> 00:15:30,450
Love is precious,

241
00:15:30,569 --> 00:15:32,010
but life is more important.

242
00:15:32,450 --> 00:15:33,929
I was with Lu Zhiyu

243
00:15:34,130 --> 00:15:35,330
because of vanity.

244
00:15:36,010 --> 00:15:37,490
I truly believe

245
00:15:38,130 --> 00:15:38,929
you're a better match

246
00:15:39,610 --> 00:15:40,409
for him.

247
00:15:43,250 --> 00:15:44,330
Then you call him.
